      <hedline>
        <hl1>Honor for Leiter</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Steve Popper</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Popper, Steve</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>New York Mets pitcher Al Leiter is recipient of 2000 Roberto Clemente Award, given to major league player who combines skills on field with sense of civic responsibility (S)</p>
      </abstract>
